    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46), a quintessential driver\u2019s car featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This unit delivers linear power through a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and the Vanos system has been meticulously serviced to ensure variable valve timing remains precise. The suspension maintains its original geometry with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback expected of the M-chassis. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic road wear consistent with its 'good' status, the powertrain and drivetrain are dialed in for peak performance. Interior features Black Nappa leather with minimal bolster wear, and the cooling system has been overhauled with a high-flow water pump and aluminum radiator.",
