      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained driver. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, with the paint showing only minor, expected stone chips on the front fascia from highway use. The alloy wheels are in great shape, wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a non-smoker environment; the premium leather seats are supple and free of tears, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound\u2014it has benefited from regular synthetic oil changes and a recent brake service. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts precisely without hesitation. It comes with a complete service history and two sets of keys. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for many more miles of enjoyment.",
